               int num_sat,
               int eph,
               int epv)
        Class constructor.
        Parameters:
        fix - 0-1: no fix, 2: 2D fix, 3: 3D fix
        num_sat - number of visible satellites
        eph - GPS horizontal dilution of position (HDOP)
        epv - GPS vertical dilution of position (VDOP)
